text: Serena Williams and her sister Venus Williams were the defending champions, but as a result of a foot injury Serena withdrew from the competition. Vania King and Yaroslava Shvedova defeated Liezel Huber and Nadia Petrova, 2–6, 6–4, 7–6(4) in the final. == Seeds == # Gisela Dulko / Flavia Pennetta (Quarterfinals) # Liezel Huber / Nadia Petrova (Final) # Nuria Llagostera Vives / María José Martínez Sánchez (First Round) # Květa Peschke / Katarina Srebotnik (Third Round) # Lisa Raymond / Rennae Stubbs (Quarterfinals) # Vania King / Yaroslava Shvedova (Champions) # Chan Yung-jan / Zheng Jie (Semifinals) # Anabel Medina Garrigues / Yan Zi (Second Round) 9.
